    "description": "这是一款有趣的休闲竞速游戏。它融合了马里奥赛车和跑跑卡丁车等卡丁车游戏的优点。不但拥有更优秀的操作手感，还拥有更丰富的玩法和更有趣的机制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/a7e8967edde9cb91884f8cb86ec7e367.webp?t=1772176598\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/cab4e1c37d53b01a8bf30f50ce4d3cdd.poster.avif?t=1772176598\" width=614 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/cab4e1c37d53b01a8bf30f50ce4d3cdd.webm?t=1772176598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/cab4e1c37d53b01a8bf30f50ce4d3cdd.mp4?t=1772176598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>这是基于物理的卡丁车，带来非常舒适的漂移手感和令人刺激的速度感。通过漂移获得氮气进行加速，这是非常高级的技巧，可以将卡丁车和赛道的优势发挥到极致。不停的打磨自己的漂移和加速技巧，调整通过弯道的策略，去追求最佳的赛道成绩吧！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/c81492190291989fba590864f230ad88.webp?t=1772176598\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/c9acdedac68dd02862d8af1a8707b600.avif?t=1772176598\" width=614 height=554 /></span><br><strong>很多个可爱的角色可选，每个角色都有两个独一无二的战斗技能。在道具比赛中，角色可以使用战斗技能或者获取随机的道具，击败其他对手也是取胜的一种方式！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/d791b2dd5b230652fce8c0e1a25e11bd.webp?t=1772176598\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/1c5af60a4898b8f42dac8eb915917d19.poster.avif?t=1772176598\" width=614 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/1c5af60a4898b8f42dac8eb915917d19.webm?t=1772176598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/1c5af60a4898b8f42dac8eb915917d19.mp4?t=1772176598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每一个赛道都有自己独特的路线特点。不同的赛道有不同的陷阱需要玩家躲避，同时也有很多隐藏的捷径可供玩家探索。根据赛道的路线特点和特殊机制来改变竞速策略，是竞速水平提升的重要手段。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/fb10f7afa91f14406df5a679bfb4cd31.webp?t=1772176598\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/e3e5c1906f2dd25f5f72a3e94290e443.avif?t=1772176598\" width=614 height=344 /></span><br><strong>有专门为新手玩家设计的技巧进阶训练。有氮气竞速模式的奖杯大赛。有角色战斗和道具玩法的奖杯大赛。有追求刷新更快记录的时间试炼赛。有限定了条件的关卡挑战赛。</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/d286a0fab0fcbc38a622122360263c72.webp?t=1772176598\" width=620 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399430/extras/eb8844c7d10be2c7118d0a74db134d30.avif?t=1772176598\" width=614 height=344 /></span><br><strong>支持本地2人、3人、4人分屏同玩，在本地多人分屏模式下，游戏的帧率几乎不会降低！利用Steam的Remote Play Together功能，你可以从好友列表直接邀请好友一起玩！</strong>",
